ComicInfo.Summary:
A while ago, Scud was given the assignment that started it all: terminate a monster named Jeff. Then came the mob. Drywall. Nathan Twist. Voo-Doo Ben. HORSE. The battles he fought. And the victories lost.
Now, as Scud stands alone, he must now finally overcome the obstacles throughout the series, if he has the strength to do it, and end the nightmare he started once and for all.
Don't miss out on the stunning conclusion to Rob Schrab's biggest series in comic history.
ComicInfo.Title: Death of the Over-Used Muse
